It's just, I look around at you and Mom and everyone getting all curbobbled.

94
00:07:27,088 --> 00:07:30,023
你不觉得夸张吗？
Doesn't this seem superfluous?

95
00:07:30,091 --> 00:07:31,080
爸爸！
Dad!

96
00:07:31,878 --> 00:07:33,547
Dad!

97
00:07:35,697 --> 00:07:38,928
