00:07:46,741 --> 00:07:48,470
鬼灵精？好可怕！
"Grinch? Oh, no!"

101
00:07:50,178 --> 00:07:52,772
是谁在说鬼灵精？
Did someone just say, "Grinch"?

102
00:07:53,781 --> 00:07:55,442
镇长大人，您好
Hello, Mayor May-Who, sir.

103
00:07:58,822 --> 00:07:59,864
Lou.

104
00:08:03,992 --> 00:08:07,018
